2
00:00:14,420 --> 00:00:17,420
=Episode 16 A Trip of the Three=

3
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:47,680
Master.

4
00:00:52,590 --> 00:00:54,590
Master, why are you back so early?

5
00:01:07,230 --> 00:01:08,270
I missed you.

6
00:01:14,310 --> 00:01:15,590
Have you got better?

7
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,160
Much better.

8
00:01:24,270 --> 00:01:26,630
I'll get a glass of water from
the kitchen and take medicine.

9
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,340
Dad.

10
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:33,180
You're back.

11
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:35,580
Why did you come back suddenly?

12
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:37,100
I met a girl at the party,

13
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:38,300
who asked to come back with me.

14
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:39,300
I just got rid of her.

15
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:40,700
A girl?

16
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:10,140
You're a grown man now.

17
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,580
Why are you still so playful?

18
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:19,980
I'm tired.

19
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,700
I'm going to take a break.

20
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,260
Let me help you.

21
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,300
So you put it in my purse

22
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:35,580
the day you took me away.

23
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:38,460
(No.)

24
00:03:39,180 --> 00:03:40,700
(I can't tell him yet.)

25
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,300
(I shouldn't get him involved.)

26
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:17,230
♪Look back♪

27
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:20,070
♪At yesterday's crabapple♪

28
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:22,790
♪Bathing in the morning light♪

29
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:25,780
(What's your purpose)

30
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,340
(by disguising yourself as Du Xunyu?)

31
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:31,220
(Did you recognize me?)

32
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,070
♪The door left ajar♪

33
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:37,420
Mistress Jiang, I'm so sorry.

34
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:38,580
No worries.

35
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:39,940
Get back to work.

36
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:44,160
♪Think of you morning and night♪

37
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,180
Here.

38
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:50,350
♪Your song lingers in the room♪

39
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:52,820
Thanks.

40
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,300
Did I mishear you?

41
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:58,500
You never say thanks.

42
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:01,820
(Thank you for all you've done,)

43
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:04,060
(Shen Xingzhi.)

44
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,720
♪I always think♪

45
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:13,560
♪By your side, I was like in paradise♪

46
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:17,790
♪I once thought time was slow♪

47
00:05:18,230 --> 00:05:20,840
♪We have years ahead of us♪

48
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:21,600
You first.

49
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:25,110
♪The lovers would always be together♪

50
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,020
You first.

51
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:29,000
♪The world♪

52
00:05:40,260 --> 00:05:41,180
Morning.

53
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:44,780
Master, morning.

54
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:45,900
Morning, Dad.

55
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:48,300
Let me see.

56
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:55,660
Fortunately, you're well now.

57
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,060
Otherwise,

58
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,780
I can't take you out.

59
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:00,660
Where do you want to take me?

60
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:02,780
Sit.

61
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:08,260
Dad, you just came back.

62
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,180
Where are you going again?

63
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,100
The orphanage our company funded

64
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,780
is officially operational.

65
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,500
So,

66
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,100
we need to go see the children.

67
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:22,620
(Does he suspect Susu's identity)

68
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:24,900
(and intend to take her away?)

69
00:06:26,340 --> 00:06:26,940
Dad.

70
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:29,460
When the orphanage
is open to the public,

71
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:31,300
there must be lots of reporters.

72
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:33,740
Mistress Jiang can't
represent the company.

73
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:35,340
Let me go with you.

74
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:41,300
Sounds right.

75
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,140
Then let's go together.

76
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:01,780
Lady first.

77
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:09,620
Dad,

78
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:10,860
the luggage has been loaded.

79
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,420
We can set off at any moment.

80
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,380
What a pity!

81
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:42,020
There's no space here.

82
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:44,540
Mistress Jiang, why don't you
go in the other car?

83
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:47,900
Ying, you can go in Xunyu's car.

84
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:49,700
OK.

85
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,380
Master,

86
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:44,860
I haven't come out with you

87
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:47,300
like this for a long time.

88
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:04,900
Why does he have to
force me to the orphanage?

89
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:06,540
It's a waste of my time.

90
00:09:10,740 --> 00:09:12,260
Even if you don't go,

91
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,060
when Du Jingchuang is home,

92
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:14,900
you can't do anything

93
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,500
under his nose.

94
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,500
Wait for another chance.

95
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,260
I don't have so much time to wait.

96
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:26,020
I'm sorry.

97
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:28,100
I... I wasn't mad at you.

98
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:32,900
Did you say sorry to me?

99
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,380
What's wrong with you recently?

100
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:46,540
What's going on?

101
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,420
Young Master pulled over.

102
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,260
Go and check.

103
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:51,620
OK.

104
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:03,940
What's wrong, Young Master?

105
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,980
There's something wrong with the car.

106
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:11,700
I assume

107
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,860
it takes a while to fix it.

108
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:16,020
Will you tell Dad about it

109
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:18,220
and ask him to go first?

110
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:26,980
Sir,

111
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,980
Young Master's car broke down.

112
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:30,020
So...

113
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,820
Tell him to fix it first.

114
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:34,300
What about Mistress Jiang?

115
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:35,380
Mistress Jiang...

116
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:36,460
Master,

117
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,940
isn't it too crowded

118
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,620
if she joins us?

119
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:42,620
Go tell Xunyu,

120
00:10:43,020 --> 00:10:45,340
they can hit the road
after fixing the car.

121
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:46,700
OK.

122
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,700
Mr. Du has some business to handle.

123
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,980
Mistress Jiang,

124
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:53,860
you can go with Young Master later.

125
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,740
Are they really leaving?

126
00:11:05,260 --> 00:11:06,380
Get the car fixed first.

127
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:22,510
♪The street covered by snow♪

128
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:26,540
It's almost winter now.

129
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:28,980
Why is it still so hot?

130
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:36,990
♪Like a disorderly movie♪

131
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:44,630
♪When we met again after years♪

132
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:51,390
♪Your smile hasn't changed♪

133
00:11:52,990 --> 00:11:58,500
♪Only there's less innocence
in your eyes♪

134
00:11:58,540 --> 00:11:59,780
What's wrong?

135
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:02,140
So cool.

136
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:03,700
Is the wind rising?

137
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,860
There was a gust of wind.

138
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,180
I thought you were

139
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:13,700
