140
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:17,180
How could I? Get back to your work.

141
00:12:20,070 --> 00:12:24,160
♪If life was still as when we first met♪

142
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:26,420
How I wish the wind

143
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:27,690
