144
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:33,680
♪If we hugged like that night♪

145
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:35,260
The front.

146
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:42,150
♪Miss you like I'm in a windowless room♪

147
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:43,620
How's that?

148
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:45,340
Cool.

149
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:03,480
♪Overlook the whistling wind
in the sea of clouds♪

150
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,800
♪The afterglow of the sunset
is in your eyes♪

151
00:13:06,950 --> 00:13:08,800
♪Rosy clouds and a swan goose♪

152
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:11,600
♪Climb over a Peak♪

153
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:17,920
♪Thousands of
unspoken vows and pledges♪

154
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:21,310
♪Nobody cherishes monsoons
and migratory birds♪

155
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:27,430
♪Travelers are not touched;
singers don't sing praises♪

156
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:31,720
♪If you accompanied me
through the hasty past♪

157
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,510
♪You must've stayed bravely♪

158
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:35,990
♪For me when young♪

159
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:39,190
♪Sand washed away♪

160
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:42,510
♪The desert becomes an oasis♪

161
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:46,920
♪Your love is a ray
in the vast sea of stars♪

162
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:49,870
♪Shining on me instantly♪

163
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:53,550
♪Like the sea embracing the sky♪

164
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:57,160
♪Like a roc swimming in the rainbow♪

165
00:13:57,550 --> 00:14:00,190
♪If love means in a confusing dream♪

166
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:01,550
♪To embrace you♪

167
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:04,720
♪To walk by the hasty past with you♪

168
